AMEND S e n ate Bill No. 2454* House Bill No. 2511
by deleting all language after the enacting clause and substituting instead:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 9-4-5107(a), is amended by adding
the language "by a regional airport authority under § 42-3-104(a)(3), by a metropolitan airport
authority under title 42, chapter 4," immediately after the language "by the housing development
agency in title 13,".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect July 1, 2026, the public welfare requiring it.
